  "title": "ISic003135. I.Sicily inscription 003135",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰεναρία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰεναρία\"><span data-text=\"Ἰεναρία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰανουαρία\">Ἰεναρία</span></span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριακός\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριακός\"><span data-text=\"Κυριακός\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Κυριακός\">Κυριακός</span></span></span> Σ☧Ω <br id=\"al2a-interpretive\">figure, zoomorphic </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Ἰεναρία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰανουαρία\">Ἰεναρία</span>  <span data-text=\"Κυριακός\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Κυριακός\">Κυριακός</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰεναρία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰεναρία\"><span data-text=\"Ἰεναρία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰανουαρία\">ΙΕΝΑΡΙΑ</span></span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριακός\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριακός\"><span data-text=\"Κυριακός\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Κυριακός\">ΚΥΡΙΑΚΟΣ</span></span></span>Σ☧Ω<br id=\"al2a-diplomatic\">figure, zoomorphic</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Ἰεναρία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἰανουαρία\">ΙΕΝΑΡΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"Κυριακός\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Κυριακός\">ΚΥΡΙΑΚΟΣ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003135_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003135_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003135.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003135-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Agnello 1956</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The monogram in line 2 can be resolved as χριστὸς σωτήρ, for which cf. Ferrua, ASS 4-5 (1938-39), p.35-37</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 18.0396 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 1960.0461 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a>  </li><li> Agnello 1956 10 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002207\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002207</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
